{"tid":310921,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇完中國版求婚大作戰","createTime":"2017-07-06T07:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T05:34:45.000Z","uid":119080,"like":4,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7c6af6052ada6db43bf22e04d69793967cb754","tid":310921,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母勁撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初頭套劇頭幾集有D生冷感 難入局<br />\n慢慢睇睇下個人投入左就好嬲小懶次次回到過去唔知係到乜9唔表白<br />\n<br />\n最後大結局串連成套劇既回憶殺好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議巴打一集一集咁睇 睇到結尾先有和應感共嗚感<br />\n<br />\n初頭睇個心成日屌鳩佢原版11集+SP 12集改到32集<br />\n<br />\n到左結尾發現32集都唔多夠喉 好唔想佢完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係太撚好睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a9900843de58a83b808eab83a4aee798194e40","tid":310921,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdbae6d5012a18e865c41f8269f3b53a72f9fb8","tid":310921,"uid":37959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"食開屎?"},{"pid":"2d59079d575d0da0dd03804127876448eaf4f311","tid":310921,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"大陸仔?"},{"pid":"1193739f77841a8f7b57021388dd760c4ef003f8","tid":310921,"uid":42820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,